A. Shama Rao Foundation, Mangaluru, has invited entries for A. Shama Rao Memorial Outstanding Teacher Award, 2016, from teachers from across the undivided Dakshina Kannada district, who have rendered exceptional services in promoting and popularizing education at high school and pre university college levels. The award carries acash prize of Rs. 10,000, memento and a citation and it would be presented during the Foundersâ€™ Day celebrations on February 14.Teachers can obtain application forms fromwww.srinivasgroup.comand the filled-in forms sent to Secretary, A. Shama Rao Foundation, Hotel Srinivas Building, GHS Road, Mangaluru 575001 before January 27. For details, call convener A.R. Shabaraya, 0824 2274722 or 9448428200.